msgid ""
"[skull]: -X. X is the current Disturbance (to a maximum of 6).\n"
"[cultist]: -4. If you fail, draw the top card of the encounter deck. If you fail by 3 or more, that card gains peril and surge.\n"
"[tablet]: -4. For each point you fail by, you must either take 1 horror or discard 1 card from your hand.\n"
"[elder_thing]: -3. Reveal another token."
msgstr ""
