msgid "Disturbance"
msgstr "扰动指数"

msgid "The expedition's reunion on the beach is decidedly dour, underscored by the rolling fog. One of the crew members you left behind to tend the boat is dead, according to the others, she was murdered when the remaining rations were stolen by starving pilgrims. Thankfully, the <i>Cassandra</i> is intact. You have barely enough food remaining to make it to the mainland. Andy and Ruby discuss their findings as the rest of the expedition bandage wounds and begin loading the <i>Cassandra</i> for the voyage home. Once the ship is loaded, you join Andy and Ruby on the shore."
msgstr "探险队在海滩上重聚了，气氛却是不一般的阴沉，在滚滚迷雾中更是不容乐观。你留下照看船只的队员有一个死了，其他人说，是饥饿的朝圣者偷补给的时候杀了她。谢天谢地，卡珊德拉号还完好无损。你们的食物差不多刚刚够回到大陆。安迪和露比在讨论自己的发现，而探险队其他队员则在包扎伤口，往卡珊德拉号上装卸，准备启程回家。等东西都装好，你加入了海岸上安迪和露比的讨论。"

msgid "Check the campaign log."
msgstr "检查剧本日志。"

msgid "If at least 1 artifact is checked under \"Artifacts Earned\""
msgstr "如果在“取得的神器”下有至少1个[[神器]]打了勾，"

msgid "...and at least 10 glyphs are translated in the glyph record:"
msgstr "……且字符记录部分翻译了至少10个字符："

msgid ""
"\"Just how much of that ugly chicken scratch did you decode?\" Ruby asks. Andy is hunched over the obsidian slate, making notes in a leatherbound notebook. In the evening half-light, the glyphs on the slate glow like pale fire. Andy leafs through several waterlogged pages and places a bloody slip of paper on the stone. \"Enough to decode this. I found it on the body of one of the pilgrims. It roughly translates to this,\" he hastily scribbles the translation on a fresh page and holds it out to you. It reads:"
"<center><fancy>\"That is not dead which can eternal lie</fancy></center>"
"<center><fancy>and with strange aeons even death may die.\"</fancy></center>"
msgstr ""
"“你认出了多少个难看的鬼画符啊？”露比问道，安迪埋头于一块黑曜石碑匾，在皮封的笔记本上记录着。碑匾上的字符发着光，在昏暗的晚上就像微弱的火焰。安迪掀开几张被水泡过的书页，把一张沾了血迹的纸放在石头上。“足够解密了。我是在一个朝圣者尸体上找到的。大概可以这么翻译。”他翻开新的一页，将翻译匆匆写在上面，交给了你。纸上写的是："
"<center><fancy>“永恒长眠的再非亡者，</fancy></center>"
"<center><fancy>在诡异的亘古中死亡亦会消逝。”</fancy></center>"

msgid "If all 5 artifacts are checked in \"Artifacts Earned,\""
msgstr "如果在“取得的神器”下全部5个[[神器]]都打了勾，"

msgid "...all 26 glyphs are translated in the glyph record,"
msgstr "……且全部26个字符都已翻译，"

msgid "...and <i>the inner sanctum was unsealed:</i>"
msgstr "……且<i>内部圣堂的封印已解除：</i>"

msgid "Add a 0 token to the chaos bag for the remainder of the campaign"
msgstr "在混乱袋中加入一个0标记，直到剧本结束。"

msgid ""
"With your own account, Ruby and Andy help you slowly piece together a narrative across the various friezes and artifacts found in the ancient city. A common theme emerges: an alien civilization from far beyond the stars, an ancient war before history itself, the sinking of R'lyeh, the \"death\" and prophesied return of an ancient god named <b><i>Cthulhu</i></b>."
"Andy points to the central spire. The obsidian gates in the base are swung wide open. A faint but sharp smell of decay wafts out of them. \"The crew members who stayed behind say those doors opened a week ago. Someone went inside, but they never returned,\" Andy says. He shares a few translations he made of rubbings from the gate. \"This one describes a glorious rebirth, a risen sleeper, and the return of the great old ones. It claims he will take back what is his: every part of R'lyeh that was stolen, every corner of his domain.\""
"\"This thing—Cthulhu—is dead. Or asleep. I'm not sure; the details are hazy at best. But with the city and everything else in it awakening, I imagine it's only a matter of time until he awakens as well. He's called followers here from their dreams. And judging by the smell, he's in <i>there</i>,\" the reporter points to the obsidian gates."
"After a long pause, Ruby stands up."
"\"It wouldn't be much of a heist if we left the doors open,\" she winks. I say we lock this thing up before we sail off into the sunset. Who's with me?\""
msgstr ""
"凭着自己的记忆，加上安迪和露比的帮助，你慢慢地拼凑出了古城中几处壁缘和神器上讲述的故事，其中浮现出一个共同的主题：远方星辰所在的异星文明；一场史前的远古战争；拉莱耶的沉没；名为<b><i>克苏鲁</i></b>的古神之“死”和预言中的回归。"
"安迪指向中心的尖塔，塔底的黑曜石大门现已敞开。里面传来微弱但刺鼻的腐败气味。“待在后方的船员说，门是在一周前打开的。有人进去了，但就没回来。”安迪说道。他分享了几句从门上拓下来的译文：“这描述了一场光荣的重生，苏醒的沉睡者，旧日支配者的回归。据称他将会夺回属于他的一切：拉莱耶被窃取的每个部分，他领域的每个角落。”"
"“这个东西—克苏鲁—已经死了，或是睡着了，我不确定，最清楚的地方细节也看不清。但既然城市和里面的一切都在苏醒，我想他醒来也只是时间的问题。他在梦里唤醒了追随者。从气味来看，他就在这里。”[[记者]]指向了黑曜石大门。"
"漫长的沉默之后，露比站了起来："
"“要是我们就这么把门开着，那也不算什么大盗了。”她眨眨眼，“我说咱们得在扬帆远航之前把这东西锁起来。谁跟我一起？”"

msgid "<i>\"We should know better than to disturb whatever is inside.\"</i>"
msgstr "<i>“无论里面是什么，我们最好不要打扰。”</i>"

msgid "Each investigator marks 1 progress under their Task in your Campaign Log. In your Campaign Log, record <i>the investigators did not confront the nightmare</i>. Proceed to <b>Interlude III: The Awakening</b>."
msgstr "在剧本日志中，每位调查员的任务下记录1进展。在剧本日志中，记录下<i>调查员没有直面梦魇</i>。进入<b>幕间故事IⅢ：苏醒</b>。"

msgid "the investigators did not confront the nightmare."
msgstr "调查员没有直面梦魇。"

msgid "<i>\"We should lay it to rest... permanently\"</i>"
msgstr "<i>“我们应该让它安息…直到永远。”</i>"

msgid "Proceed to <b>Setup</b>"
msgstr "进入<b>设置</b>"

msgid "Put Dreamer's Rest and each copy of Sigil-Carved Alcove into play."
msgstr "将入梦者之墓和每张咒刻凹室放置入场。"

msgid "Each investigator begins play at Dreamer's Rest."
msgstr "每位调查员从入梦者之墓开始游戏。"

msgid "In player order, each player may choose 1 [[Item]] asset from the <i>Expedition</i> encounter set to begin in play under their control. This set is indicated by the following icon:"
msgstr "按玩家顺序，每位玩家可以从<i>探险</i>遭遇组选择1张[[道具]]支援，使其位于自己控制之下开始游戏。该遭遇组的图标为："

msgid "Gather all earned [[Artifact]] assets and put each of them into play under an investigator's control, divided as evenly as possible."
msgstr "收齐所有取得的[[神器]]支援，将它们放置入场，位于调查员控制之下，尽可能平均分配。"

msgid "Build a special agenda deck using Beneath the City as the first agenda and Cthulhu Awakened as the second agenda. These replace the act and agenda decks."
msgstr "创建一个特殊密谋牌库，其中“城市之下”是第一张密谋，“克苏鲁苏醒”是第二张密谋。这替代了场景和密谋牌库。"

msgid "Throughout this scenario, the number of resources under \"Disturbance\" on the scenario reference card indicate Cthulhu's awareness of the investigators. The higher the Disturbance, the closer the Sleeper is to awakening. Disturbance has no inherent game effect on its own; however, some encounter card effects may change or become stronger depending on the current level of Disturbance."
msgstr "本场冒险中，冒险参考卡牌的“扰动指数”下方的资源数表示克苏鲁有无发觉调查员。扰动指数越高，沉睡者越接近苏醒。扰动指数本身没有游戏效果；但是，某些遭遇卡牌根据当前扰动指数，可能会改变或变得更强。"

msgid "Each investigator who was defeated is driven <b>insane</b>. If there are no surviving investigators, the investigators lose the campaign."
msgstr "每位被击败的调查员发疯。如果没有幸存的调查员，则调查员剧本失败。"

msgid "the investigators halted Cthulhu's awakening."
msgstr "调查员阻止了克苏鲁的苏醒。"

msgid "Each investigator earns 10 bonus experience, as they prevented an ancient evil from rising to terrorize all of the earth once again."
msgstr "每位调查员取得10点奖励经验值，因为其阻止世界因为远古恶魔的苏醒而再度陷入恐怖。"

msgid "Each investigator suffers 2 mental trauma."
msgstr "每位调查员承受2点精神创伤。"

msgid "Broken in both mind and body, you collapse before the great form of Cthulhu. All around you the city quakes, filling your ears with a deafening drone. Cthulhu stares down at you with indifference. You are nothing more to him than a nuisance, an insignificant pest. Your consciousness soon folds in on itself as the frail structure of your mind gives way to the unbound freedom of utter insanity."
msgstr "你身心俱裂，在克苏鲁的伟大形体前倒下了。四周的城市在颤动，你耳中全是嗡鸣，几乎将你震聋。克苏鲁冷漠地俯视着你。你对他而言不过是一个小小的妨碍，一只无关紧要的小虫。你的意志很快就开始塌缩，你脆弱的思维已经崩渍，取而代之的，是无拘无束的彻底疯狂。"

msgid ""
"The gargantuan form of Cthulhu falls backwards into the central pool His flabby clawed hands grasp at the edges of the pool, failing to find purchase, as his form sinks below the black water. The five glowing red eyes, distorted by the water's surface, slowly fade from view. And, just as suddenly as it started, all is quiet and still."
"You emerge from the obsidian gates and walk to the edge of the shoreline. At long last, you're ready to leave this city behind, bring these artifacts back to Arkham, and move on with your life. As you climb aboard the <i>Cassandra</i>, you look back at the blasphemous skyline, outlined against the setting sun like the spine of an ancient beast. The turbid waters churn as the ancient city begins to descend, almost imperceptibly, to be reclaimed by the ocean. Both the dreamer and his house in R'lyeh have been laid to rest."
"\"I wonder what Mr Tillinghast planned to do with those artifacts,\" Andy muses. \"Probably sell 'em\" Ruby says, a cigarette clenched between her teeth. Closing your eyes, you turn back to the cabin. Perhaps tonight, for the first time in months, you'll enjoy a deep, dreamless sleep."
msgstr ""
"克苏鲁的巨大形体向后倒去，栽进了中央的大池。他带爪的巨手没能抓牢池子边缘，整个身子沉入了黑水之中。那五只红眼发出的光，在水面下扭曲，渐渐黯淡不见。一切重归寂静，就像来的一样突然。"
"你走出黑曜石大门，来到海岸边缘。你终于准备离开这座城市，带着神器返回阿卡姆，继续你的生活。你爬上<i>卡珊德拉号</i>，回望了一眼这里亵渎的天际线，在落日的勾勒下仿佛一只远古巨兽的脊背。浑浊的海水搅动起来，古城开始缓缓下沉，慢得几乎无法察觉，但它终将重归大洋。拉莱耶的入梦者和他的居所又将安息。"
"“我想知道蒂林哈斯特先生打算拿这些神器干什么。”安迪沉思道。“可能是卖了吧。”露比已经叼了根烟。你闭上眼，回到船舱。也许今晚，几个月来第一次，你终于能享受一次无梦的深度睡眠。"
